Replace the repository copies of these files with the files in 
this directory. 

Use a single SC telescope as the array.

The code will draw a limited number of tracks on an opengl drawing 
of the SC telescope. Change the number of tracks to plot a different
number. The code snipet is from GSCTelescope.cpp

  if (manager->GetNtracks() == 27) {
    manager->DrawTracks();
  }
